    Page: 243
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=On Judging Others
By: St Catherine of Siena
---
One thing thou must do in order to arrive at this union, this purity,
is to abstain from judging the will of man in anything at all that
thou findest said or done, no matter by what creature, whether against
thee, whether against another.
